These polynomials satisfy (18.22.2) with <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C18.S22.Px2.p1.m1">p_{n}(x)</Math> , <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C18.S22.Px2.p1.m2">A_{n}</Math> , and <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C18.S22.Px2.p1.m3">C_{n}</Math> as in Table 18.22.1.
</sentence>

</para>
         
